疾病稀有性的划分視乎被研究的人群。任何一种癌症在儿童身上都非常罕见<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ecpc-online.org/newsletter/member-updates/168-rare-cancer-day.html |title=02/2009: Rare Cancers on Rare Disease Day |publisher=Ecpc-online.org |date=2009-02-28 |accessdate=2012-09-24 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726131436/http://www.ecpc-online.org/newsletter/member-updates/168-rare-cancer-day.html |archivedate=2011-07-26 }}</ref>，但部分类型的癌症在成人身上卻非常常见。

